lead_paragraph: The Chicago Cubs and Cleveland Indians sat through a 17-minute rain delay before resuming Game 7 of the World Series in the 10th inning with the score tied at 6 early Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Rain Delays World Series Game 7 With Cubs, Indians Tied at 6
